<p>
Must have a technology centric background that includes significant customer interaction. A minimum of 5 - 7 years experience as a sales director is required. Professionals who have successfully created sustainable competitive advantage by tuning channel strategies and attaining high individual performance will be considered most favorably. The candidate must have previous experience working at senior staff levels with a peer group consisting of other highly seasoned professionals.</p>
<p>
International Sales Director</p>
